translation: գայթակղել / հրապուրել (հաճախ՝ բացասական կամ սեռական ենթատեքստով)
description:
• 1. Attract sexually or romantically:
“To tempt someone into a sexual or romantic relationship, often by charm or persuasion.”
— Example: “He tried to seduce her with compliments and charm.”

• 2. Persuade to do something wrong or unwise:
“To lure someone into doing something they normally wouldn’t.”
— Example: “She was seduced by the promise of easy money.”
